This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder "VDR", see http://www.tvdr.de/.

Written by:                    Jasmin Jessich <jasmin@anw.at> (2013-2017)
                               Winfried Koehler <nvdec A.T. quantentunnel D.O.T. de > (2021 and later)

